                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350406-name-1026" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350406-name-1026" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350406-name-1026" type="surname" value="ROGERS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350406-name-1026" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>ELIZABETH ROGERS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of William Rogers, of Phipp-street. The prisoner came to lodge with me on the 30th of October—he left on the 20th of January—he had the first-floor back room—these articles were in the room—after he had left me two days I opened the room, which he had left locked, and missed the counterpane, bolster, and blankets.</p>
               <p>
